text: Sabine Kottig is a German water polo player. She was part of the German women's national water polo team at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships and 2001 Women's European Water Polo Championship. == References == == Other websites == * german-katrin-dierolf? getty * frances-myriam-argaud-and- germanys-sabine-kottig getty category:German water polo players Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
